      • main

        public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)
        Stores the Madlib as a single string. Calls the method for each part of speech. For each call of a method (Noun, Adjective, etc.), the string result becomes the result of the call of the previous method and is passed to the next method.
        Parameters:
        args - Main method does not accept input from args.
